# Backend Agent Rules

- One agent per file under `backend/agents/`
- Agents are pure functions: `def run(state: RaidState) -> dict`
- Use tools from `backend/tools/` — never call sponsor APIs directly in agents
- Append to `agent_events` on start and completion
- Return only changed keys (LangGraph merge)
- JSON from LLMs: parse with try/except; fail gracefully with logged error event
- No blocking sleeps in graph nodes
